# MK8D boot reference trace from zuyu/yuzu
# Window: first ~5s of startup
# Purpose: compact baseline for comparing ruzu against upstream behavior
#
# Source logs:
# - traces/zuyu_full_5s_trace.log
#   Contains timestamps, SVC_IN/SVC_OUT, scheduler transitions, IPC calls.
# - traces/zuyu_mk8d_svc_trace.txt
#   Contains denser SVC decoding, TLS request/response dumps, CreateThread/StartThread markers.
#
# Selection policy:
# - keep representative boot scheduler transitions
# - keep representative SVC IN/OUT pairs
# - keep all high-signal thread bootstrap markers around CreateThread/StartThread
# - keep the worker-thread entry pattern at PC=0x01D31B18
#
# Notes:
# - This is a derived reference file, not the canonical raw capture.
# - For full-detail comparison, fall back to the two source traces above.

