== What to compare against in ruzu ==
- Same early SCHED cadence around tid=75 and idle-thread hops.
- Same SVC imm=0x08/0x09 pairs for worker creation/start.
- Same worker entry point PC=0x01D31B18 recurring during bootstrap.
- Same first scheduling handoff to core=1 after worker start.
- Same presence of SleepThread (imm=0x0b) on worker threads after bootstrap.
